pub fun capture-error[12,9,12,21] : forall<a,(e :: E)> (action : () -> <(std/core/types/handled :: ((E, V) -> V) -> X)<(std/core/exn/exn :: (E, V) -> V)>|(e :: E)> a) -> (e :: E) (std/core/exn/error :: V -> V)<a>;
 
